title: Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei - Deep Snow (Doujinshi)
description:
Miyuki loves her older brother... REALLY loves in fact... Once she hears about his getting married to a classmate of there's Miyuki sets out to seduce him... and so begins a rather sweet, incestuous, story.

A compilation of issues 1-6 has been published in full-volume (tankoubon) form, called Deep Snow Soushuuen.
